      %h2 Who we are
      %p.section-description.lead
        Skorpion Software is a group of passionate developers who believe that all businesses can maximize their online potential through expertly developed mobile and web applications for strategic marketing. We seek to solve real problems through a seamless digital experience. We are a company that keeps up-to-date on technology to ensure that businesses are provided with the most current and applicable web solutions to meet their needs.
        %br>/
        We are the digital solutions company for startups, agencies, and enterprises.
      %h2 What we do
      %p.section-description.lead
        We create web-based products with synergy between the needs of the business and the profile of the customers. We take your ideas and needs and develop the right solution for you. At Skorpion Software, our people help you make a difference in your business by building quality websites and web applications and engaging in quantifiable SEO strategies.
      %h2 Why choose us
      %p.section-description.lead
        We are a team passionate about what we do and about helping businesses to succeed. We believe in delivering exceptional customer service and support, and in producing results from start to finish. We listen to and work closely with our clients to ensure that the final products are always as required to enhance their business.
      %h3
        Contact Skorpion Software today to discuss how our web solutions can empower your business.
